00061 class OplEntry 
00062 {
00063     public:
00064         enum {
00065             c_opl_buffer_len = 8
00066         };
00067 
00068         OplEntry(const UINT8 * buffer) { memcpy(m_buffer,buffer,c_opl_buffer_len); }
00069 
00070     // content is define in 3GPP TS 31.102 4.2.59
00071         BOOLEAN IsBcdPlmnMatching(BcdPlmn checkplmn) const { 
00072             return StackWrapper::IsBcdPlmnMatching(checkplmn,((UINT16)m_buffer[0]<<8)+m_buffer[1],m_buffer[2]);
00073         }
00074         UINT16  GetLacLow() const { return ((UINT16)m_buffer[3]<<8) + m_buffer[4]; }
00075         UINT16  GetLacHigh() const { return ((UINT16)m_buffer[5]<<8) + m_buffer[6]; }
00076         BOOLEAN HasEntireLacRange() const { return GetLacLow()==0x0000 && GetLacHigh()==0xFFFE; }
00077         INT     GetPnnRecordId() { return (INT)m_buffer[7]; }
00078         BOOLEAN HasPnnRecordId() const { return m_buffer[7]!=0x00 && m_buffer[7]!=0xFF; }
00079         
00080 
00081         UINT8 m_buffer[c_opl_buffer_len];
00082 };

00099 // is for internal use only, holds the Mexe descriptor entries of the SIM/USIM of the ORPK,ARPK,TPRPK
00100 // files in the DF-Mexe directory
00101 class MexeDescriptor 
00102 {
00103     public:
00104         MexeDescriptor(MexeCertType type, const UINT8 * buffer, UINT16 len) {
00105             ASSERT_DEBUG(len>=10);
00106             m_length = len;     
00107             m_type = type;
00108             m_buffer = new UINT8[len];
00109             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0);
00110             memcpy(m_buffer,buffer,len); 
00111         }
00112 
00113         ~MexeDescriptor() {
00114             delete[] m_buffer;
00115             m_buffer = 0;
00116             m_length = 0;
00117         }
00118 
00119         MexeCertType GetMexeCertType() const { 
00120             return m_type;
00121         }
00122 
00123     // content is defined in 3GPP TS 51.011 10.4.4.2
00124     
00125         BOOLEAN IsValid() const { 
00126             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (*m_buffer & 0x01)==0x00;
00127         }
00128         
00129         BOOLEAN IsAuthorityCert() const { 
00130             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (m_buffer[1] & 0x01)==0x01;
00131         }
00132         
00133         UINT GetCertType() const { 
00134             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (UINT)(m_buffer[2]);
00135         }
00136 
00137         SimFileId GetSimFileId() const { 
00138             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (SimFileId)((m_buffer[3]<<8)+m_buffer[4]);
00139         }
00140 
00141         UINT16 GetCertOffset() const { 
00142             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (UINT16)((m_buffer[5]<<8)+m_buffer[6]);
00143         }
00144 
00145         UINT16 GetCertLength() const { 
00146             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (UINT16)((m_buffer[7]<<8)+m_buffer[8]);
00147         }
00148 
00149         UINT8 GetKeyIdLength() const { 
00150             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); return (m_buffer[9]);
00151         }
00152 
00153         UINT8 * GetKeyIdBuffer() const { 
00154             ASSERT_DEBUG(m_buffer!=0); 
00155             return (GetKeyIdLength()>0) ? &m_buffer[10] : 0;
00156         }
00157 
00158     private:
00159         UINT8 *      m_buffer;
00160         UINT16       m_length;
00161         MexeCertType m_type;
00162 };
